{"tid":2170280,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羅致光：暫時沒有計劃為安老院長者進行普及檢測，但全部市民應做檢測","createTime":"2020-08-23T07:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T09:35:03.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b1c434a0592ef3d377312b65ab5d9c9bcb89476b","tid":2170280,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:11:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545347-20200823.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545347-20200823.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTDsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=67f37694\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545347-20200823.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4d9a1320\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545347-20200823.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n勞工及福利局局長羅致光表示，現時當局並沒有為安老院舍的院友進行普及病毒檢測，主要是考慮到長者的身體狀況難以外出，如果要為他們進行檢測，或需要安排他們到醫院的負氣壓房間，全港現時有超過6萬名安老院院友，屬非常龐大的工程，因此在下月推行普及社區檢測中，暫時沒有計劃包括住在安老院的長者。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光在網誌又提到，新冠病毒「狡猾」，部分患者沒有病徵，又或是病徵十分輕微仍可傳播病毒，勸喻如非必要應減少帶院舍的長者外出。而謝絕安老院舍探訪，甚或限制院友外出，都是迫不得已的「惡法」，對院友的心理健康會帶來十分大的負面影響。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，安老院舍可以善用資訊科技，協助長者與家人保持聯絡。社署會設立約1000個臨時職位，為期1年，協助安老院舍推行科技應用，以便長者與家人保持聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光又指出，為院舍員工提供免費的病毒檢測，是為了防範隱性病毒傳播者，即使不能日日檢，定期的檢測亦可以減低風險。"},{"pid":"9afa5d8555fca485f18224430eab0f2278c0ada4","tid":2170280,"uid":304916,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:12:46.000Z","msg":"老野無價值 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7fc2beb388892a45aad571b4d5df83ca81f6c1","tid":2170280,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9afa5d8555fca485f18224430eab0f2278c0ada4","tid":2170280,"uid":304916,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:12:46.000Z","msg":"老野無價值 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:13:42.000Z","msg":"人地智商180喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8490710297b0b7099f60057b5d84941eb0eb774b","tid":2170280,"uid":37596,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:14:06.000Z","msg":"廢老無監控價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c31259327cc3eaa70fb499907f5563a813b4fbec","tid":2170280,"uid":304916,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8490710297b0b7099f60057b5d84941eb0eb774b","tid":2170280,"uid":37596,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:14:06.000Z","msg":"廢老無監控價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:16:08.000Z","msg":"啲器官都唔值錢"},{"pid":"9dd5723d17c2c5fb6912bf6de7d6486d781f4ec9","tid":2170280,"uid":94241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:17:20.000Z","msg":"老人院獨立！！！"},{"pid":"cedd9535b743c4fd4ff6557d305eaffb2de22548","tid":2170280,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:17:21.000Z","msg":"廢老係負家產 驗黎冇價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39403ccdc2c29bd8af9aca635a6a20ac78f0f5d8","tid":2170280,"uid":137725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:21:54.000Z","msg":"咁即係意圖更加明顯啦"},{"pid":"48302859b3ca678958fd8b3c9b88df677455ee46","tid":2170280,"uid":229225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T09:32:55.000Z","msg":"講堅, 呢個係 &quot;德政&quot;!<br />\n點解?<br />\n因為老人院要檢測,<br />\n基本上入面既老人家無得走,<br />\n一定要做.<br />\n而老人家做咗檢測拎咗 DNA,<br />\n就等如佢地既仔仔女女, 子子孫孫既 DNA 都間接拎埋,<br />\n你話幾大鑊?"},{"pid":"989d5251e861a483a0c21accff43b9025dff1c74","tid":2170280,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T09:35:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />換血保青春"}]}